{"tid":1648101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]遊行綿羊概念必須要改","createTime":"2019-10-12T04:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T08:36:04.000Z","uid":218313,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4cacfb765e2f6f8d9397802915d64db22fa61e03","tid":1648101,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"近幾次港島遊行都完成唔到<br />\n知唔知點解呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為你地見前面有防暴狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有TG<br />\n成條隊就on99 企定係度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非到左呢一刻<br />\n仲執著於民陣式既大遊行<br />\n即跟大隊跟路線<br />\n前面停，你又停，行唔到就企定定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班狗就俾睇中左和理非=一班綿羊<br />\n只要一截左個頭，成班無人帶<br />\n就截開你地慢慢食<br />\n<br />\n唔該，下次見條隊停左俾度<br />\n有大聲公個D必須要大叫<br />\nBe Water <br />\n自己搵路繼續行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得口號<br />\nBe water dull 路行<br />\n<br />\n我地如果好似流水咁<br />\n班狗係無我地乎架<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"33bdc90057b8a49fde131ada99884cd89c5f35db","tid":1648101,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:51:11.000Z","msg":"用手機好難排位。。<br />\n推"},{"pid":"1a443e3c6056b853ab7346558501fa791930ffdc","tid":1648101,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:51:56.000Z","msg":"10月12日 1500 尖沙咀 反緊急法大遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/emrsnS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/emrsnS</a>"},{"pid":"52e16a8a40410f197b60305d61f7393a03604f3c","tid":1648101,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"我係陳彥霖由細玩到大既朋友 你地愈吹愈大 我好撚嬲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a3df318f98f333d25873caec289ef07ca555f68","tid":1648101,"uid":218313,"lik